OL,5,FRichard O'Callaghan, Environment
OL,6,FAgency's Area Manager, warned that a
OL,7,Ffew rain spells won't undo months of
OL,8,Fdryness, and only sustained wetter
OL,9,Fweather will restore reservoirs,
OL,10,Frivers and groundwater.
OL,12,FHe said that this particular part of
OL,13,Fthe region is struggling a lot more
OL,14,Fthan others.
