OL,5,F"Resilience in each water supply zone
OL,6,Fis different," said O'Callaghan.
OL,7,F"Droughts will affect different supply
OL,8,Fzones differently, what we're seeing
OL,9,Fhere that is a set of circumstances...
OL,10,Fhas shown there is a security of
OL,11,Fsupply challenge that has been
OL,12,Fgradually escalating over the past few
OL,13,Fmonths.
OL,15,FSouth East Water has applied for a
OL,16,Fdrought order to preserve remaining
OL,17,Fsupply, and new exemptions to the
OL,18,Fexisting hosepipe ban have been
OL,19,Fremoved.
